Package edu.wpi.cs3733d18.teamS.pathfind

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Ant
    This class is an animated "ant" that travels along a specified path repeatedly.
    AStar
    The Class manages the AStar path algorithm and primarily finds the optimal path with the lowest search time based on heuristics.
    AStarNode
    AStarNode.java Nodes that have costs and neighbors for a-star calculations
    BreadthFirst
    The Class manages the breadth First path algorithm changes and finds a path by searching outwards (not movement cost based).
    DepthFirst
    The Class manages the Depth First path algorithm changes and finds a path (**not optimal**).
    Dijkstras
    The Class manages the Dijkstras path algorithm and finds the path from a location based on lowest movement costs.
    InteractivePhone  
    Map
    This Class deals with the Map and related methods.
    Path
    Path.java Holds path information from AStar and calculates text directions.
    Pathfinder
    Pathfinder.java Loads from edu.wpi.cs3733d18.teamS.database and calculates the fastest path between given nodes.
    QRCode
    This class deals with the QR code image and methods relating to it.
    SearchAlgorithm
    The Abstract class that holds common functions for the different types of path finding algorithms.
